{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_城门汇合",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·城门汇合（终幕入口）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "flow_xungou_main",
              "state": "s12_chufa",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "apply_taoist_avatar"
    },
    "apply_taoist_avatar": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setPlayerAvatar",
          "params": {
            "animManifest": "/resources/runtime/animation/player_taoist_anim_v1/anim.json",
            "stateMap": {
              "idle": "hero_stand",
              "walk": "hero_walk",
              "run": "hero_run_new"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "雾还压着那条路。故事到这点——才刚开头。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "埃德加"
      },
      "text": "Ah，我们的向导先生！Look at you——这身行头，very 专业！（他冲克拉拉挑了挑眉）",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "克拉拉"
      },
      "text": "（上下打量了一遍那身凑合的道袍，在本子上记了一笔，什么也没说）行李齐了。Guan 先生，可以出发了吗？此行经桃溪一带——那里，Guan 先生去过吗？",
      "next": "sw_met_ltg"
    },
    "sw_met_ltg": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "met_litiangou",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "n_ltg_hook"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "c1"
    },
    "n_ltg_hook": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "桃溪嗦？老子熟得很！前几天还有个怪道士，专门来向老子打听那一带的事——那个地方，老子门清！",
      "next": "c1"
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "zou",
          "text": "「走。」（老子走在前头——莫慌，腔调要稳起）",
          "next": "n3"
        },
        {
          "id": "deng",
          "text": "「等哈。」（最后望一眼雾津城……要得，走。）",
          "next": "n3b"
        }
      ]
    },
    "n3b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他回头望了一眼。茶馆的幌子、码头的桅杆、城隍庙的飞檐——都泡在晨雾里。",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_城门汇合",
            "signal": "chufa_departed"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
